bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "preference-be"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "preference-be"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = []
keywords = []
categories = []
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
envconfig = "0.10.0"
futures = "0.3"
itertools = "0.10.2"
log = "0.4"
mongodb = "2"
pretty_env_logger = "0.4"
reqwest = "0.11"
serde_json = "1"
warp = "0.3"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = ["derive", "rc"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["full"]
optional = false

[dev-dependencies]
rstest = "0.12.0"
